        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p>This bill requires health insurers to include expenditures for activities that address social determinants of health when calculating the proportion of premium revenues spent on clinical services and quality improvement (i.e., medical loss ratio).</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
